0Z","msg":"唔知戲院餐廳情況，但可以一試"},{"pid":"8304bb4ff9413692f85bc7b4e27d4c194f3ea077","tid":2032491,"uid":108337,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T05:59:56.000Z","msg":"迫D狗周圍封路封商場最開心<br />\n藍絲同商家都要一齊受惡果"},{"pid":"09665dce2e2e202a59c424ffdba9c3df9bcda8dd","tid":2032491,"uid":304769,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:00:15.000Z","msg":"轉場，全港商場收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span>"},{"pid":"84ea44e3f141579f9ed408d48b4b5bf0b491033b","tid":2032491,"uid":81934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:00:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d0793d994bcf7f847f9edcd304aee999ff932bf","tid":2032491,"uid":207762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:00:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43eaa916d44b39672f58654995c887a85bb189e0","tid":2032491,"uid":207762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:00:35.000Z","msg":"灣仔警嫂黎緊"},{"pid":"98381a3313eb648d96f2bfa7261148762310afa1","tid":2032491,"uid":324984,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a9f34dcf3f344e00a37064914b0c2b196135090b","tid":2032491,"uid":4574,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"repl