 />\n2020-05-24 HKT 14:34<br />\n<br />\n大批市民響應網上號召，下午由銅鑼灣遊行至灣仔，警方一度施放催淚彈驅散。<br />\n<br />\n灣仔多處有人堵路，包括近修頓球場，以及伊利沙伯大廈對開的一段告士打道；亦有人破壞交通燈，警方一度在天樂里舉起橙旗。一批防暴警員增援，有警員截查一名男子時，警告他非法集結，要求出示單據證明曾到銅鑼灣購物，期間又要求在場記者後退。<br />\n<br />\n另外，水炮車及銳武裝甲車由杜老誌道駛至銅鑼灣鵝頸橋底，聚集人士向銅鑼灣方向散去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528026-20200524.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528026-20200524.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=91b3895d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528026-20200524.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=deb5935b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528026-20200524.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6e20a43276728929937808fdfa5ef636134a3978","tid":2032491,"uid":238919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:41:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">     #灣仔 <br />\n1438 灣仔站a1 A2 B1 出口落閘 </span>"},{"pid":"5be5fe3bcbaa45749a114851fe9fe60171ef25cd","tid":2032491,"uid":238919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:41:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">  #灣仔 <br />\n1440 灣仔 軒尼詩道杜老誌道交界 1裝甲車1水炮車u turn向銅鑼灣   </span>"},{"pid":"fd6512a394d92977484dc14f8fcfce65c59b97f9","tid":2032491,"uid":238919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:42:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">     #灣仔 <br />\n1440 灣仔 軒尼詩道杜老誌道交界 1裝甲車1水炮車u turn向銅鑼灣 </span></span>"}]}